---

This package vendors and compiles the following third-party C libraries under
src/third_party/. Each retains its own license:

- libxlsxwriter (https://github.com/jmcnamara/libxlsxwriter) by John McNamara,
  licensed under the BSD 2-Clause license. This package is a Dart binding to it.
- minizip (bundled with libxlsxwriter), licensed under the zlib license.
- md5 (bundled with libxlsxwriter), by the Regents of the University of
  California, BSD-style / public-domain terms.
- dtoa and tmpfileplus (bundled with libxlsxwriter), permissive terms.
- zlib (https://github.com/madler/zlib) by Jean-loup Gailly and Mark Adler,
  licensed under the zlib license.

Full license texts are in src/third_party/*/LICENSE.
